{"tid":2380301,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣創近一年半高位,夾屋855萬高價易手","createTime":"2021-01-25T18:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T04:11:39.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d417a0d453a13bebed65d7aae4bb8338d10a01","tid":2380301,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"青衣近70宗成交創近一年半以來單月高位 夾屋宏福花園海景2房以近8個月高價易手<br />\n<br />\n二手交投持續升溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單月高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同類高價易手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8個月以來高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二手交投持續升溫，青衣區本月成交迫近70宗，為自2019年4月以來單月高位，新近易手的夾屋宏福花園2房海景戶，更以近8個月以來同類高價易手。利嘉閣地產皇牌屋苑青衣灝景灣一行高級分區市務經理彭錦添表示，青衣區本月暫錄69宗成交，可望打破2019年4月71宗單月成交高位，而新近成交的夾屋宏福花園2座中層C室，實用面積598平方呎，2房，以855萬高價易手。 前臨青衣公園再享藍巴勒海景，同樣造價也可選擇區內私人屋苑的細單位，但景觀、實用程度不及上述單位，造價為同類單位近8個月以來高位，實用呎價14298元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2861696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2861696&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=e6c88e56\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2861696</a>"},{"pid":"0ae0ff633ad475a9a069306e337e0b99ea863818","tid":2380301,"uid":242102,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:41:59.000Z","msg":"拉po，不實消息0討論價值<br />\n盡量每次更新證據<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">騙徒證據 話創新高，其實低過2018</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gBfsBT